---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const links = [
  { label: "GitHub",   href: "https://github.com/JasonYeYuhe" },
  { label: "小红书",   href: "https://www.xiaohongshu.com/" },
  { label: "Email",    href: "mailto:yyyyy.yeyuhe@gmail.com" },
  { label: "RSS",      href: "/rss.xml" },
];
---
<footer class="border-t border-rule mt-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3 text-sm text-muted">
    <div>
      <p class="font-display text-base text-ink">Jason Ye</p>
      <p class="mt-1">中文 AI builder · 把一线资料做成可用的操作系统。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-ink-soft font-medium mb-2">联系</p>
      <ul class="space-y-1">
        {links.map(({ label, href }) => (
          <li><a href={href} class="hover:text-accent">{label}</a></li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-ink-soft font-medium mb-2">版权与免责</p>
      <p>本站所引第三方资料版权归各原作者所有。资料库内的译本/注解为非官方，仅供学习交流；收到权利人请求即删。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border-t border-rule">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-4 text-xs text-muted flex flex-wrap gap-x-4 gap-y-2 justify-between items-center">
      <span>© {year} Jason Ye</span>
      <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-4">
        <a href="/library" class="hover:text-accent">资料库</a>
        <a href="/os" class="hover:text-accent">OS</a>
        <a href="/writing" class="hover:text-accent">手记</a>
        <a href="/services" class="hover:text-accent">合作</a>
        <a href="/tags" class="hover:text-accent">标签</a>
      </nav>
      <span>Built with Astro · 学术克制</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
